description:
There was a fire in our house on the 2nd floor last night and we evacuated and waited outside while the fire was extinguished. Fortunately, it was extinguished quickly and the only victim survived and now she is in the hospital, only the smell reached our apartment. After that, all day I was listing why we did not take certain things, except for the most basic ones. Why didn't I take a photo camera, for example?

Today I looked at the birds for a very long time, I had the last frame in the cassette, which I could not use for several days. The birds flew up and I saw them landing on the wires. I decided that sometimes it was necessary to act in order not to regret and took a picture.
